Druheho februara = Second of February - 
tretieho marca = Third of March - 
stvrteho aprila = Fourth of April -
-piateho maja = the fifth of May - 
siesteho juna = the sixth of June - 
siedmeho = the seventh - 
osmeho augusta = the eighth of August - 
deviatho septembra = the ninth of September - 
- desiateho okotobra = the tenth of October - 
jedenasteho novembra = the eleventh of November - 
dvanasteho decembra = the twelfth of December - 
dvadsiateho marca = the twentieth of March - 
-dvadsiateho osmeho aprila = the twentieth of April - 
tridsiateho prveho maja = the thirty-first of May - 
od dvadsiateho stvrteho maja do tretieho juna = from the twenty-fourth of May to the third of June - 

What is the time?	Koľko je hodín?
It is..	Je../Sú..
o'clock	hodina/hodiny/hodín
Do you have time today?	Máš dnes čas?
Yes, I have time today.	Áno, mám dnes čas.
How late is it?	Ako neskoro je?
half	pol
quarter	štvrť
5 minutes to 12 (11:55)	o 5 minút 12 hodín
5 past 12 (12:05)	12 hodín a 5 minút
"in 5 minutes 12" (11:55)	"o 5 minút 12"
It is one o'clock.	Je jedna hodina.
It is two/three/four o'clock.	Sú dve, tri, štyri hodiny.
It is five/six/... twelve o'clock.	Je päť, šesť,... dvanásť hodín.

